# Runtime configuration (credentials live in environment variables, not in the image)
# The Dockerfile copies config.example.json (placeholder values only) as config.json.
# Real credentials are injected at runtime via TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN / TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID env vars.

